name: Home Decorators Collection Bamboo Black Room Divider
description: The Natural-Fiber Room Divider in Black from Home Decorators Collection features 3 natural fiber panels adorned with bamboo silhouettes on a sturdy pine frame with a sleek black finish. Ideal for your bedroom, living room, dining room or family room, this piece is easy to store with hinged panels that fold flat and is ready to go right out of the box with no assembly required.
